<item>
            <title>[SPARK-39910] DataFrameReader API cannot read files from hadoop archives (.har)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-39910</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Reading a file from an hadoop archive using the DataFrameReader API returns an empty Dataset:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
scala&amp;gt; val df = spark.read.textFile(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;har:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;///user/preaudc/logs/lead/jp/2022/202207.har/20220719&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;df: org.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;] = [value: string]
scala&amp;gt; df.count
res7: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Long&lt;/span&gt; = 0 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the other hand, reading the same file, from the same hadoop archive, but using the RDD API yields the correct result:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
scala&amp;gt; val df = sc.textFile(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;har:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;///user/preaudc/logs/lead/jp/2022/202207.har/20220719&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;value&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;df: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [value: string]
scala&amp;gt; df.count
res8: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Long&lt;/span&gt; = 5589 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
